{
  "stem": "9.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a whole city in-- in France-- Sherbrooke-- where the whole population in the little city decided to hide out all the Jews for no other reason but this is-- we are our brothers keepers.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's not right to have decent human beings killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was one of these very wonderful things that did happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were many more, but comparatively, a very small percentage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure-- a lot of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband used to know a lot of those people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Poland, the situation was very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the only way I can explain it is that the-- in Polish church, there were many people that were very, very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because even before the war, before Hitler started the war, there were many Polish individuals in the church that would go to Hitler and teach them about anti-Semitism, and tell them what do.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There are whole books now written-- what happened in Poland before the war when nobody knew about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody heard about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I certainly didn't know about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it did exist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I am hoping, as far as that goes-- anti-Semitism-- and right now, finally, the first step was made.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism is a disease that people have that they don't really know why-- people that have never met any Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They think Jews have horns on the head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They are some kind of outcasts-- until they meet some people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it comes, a lot of it, from the Catholic catechism, where the children are taught in the very young age that Jews killed Jesus Christ.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
